title: iPad Mini 4 Review | Awesome Stuff Week!
description:
Hey! It's Awesome Stuff Week on YouTube, a five-day celebration of awesome stuff with reviews, rants, randomness and more from me and many more of your favorite YouTubers. So check out awesome products, fashion, accessories and more—the stuff that we can't live without—in this video, and at the main playlist at http://youtube.com/AwesomeStuffWeek

Review of the new Apple iPad Mini 4, probably the most under hyped product Apple announced last month!

For behind the scenes, follow me here:
